2015-06-04 11:47:07	adsc	and develop is the localhost on each devs machine
2015-06-04 11:47:09	pid1	I work in networking, and our production servers are those that run the tools we rely on every day. We then have testing servers where we try out new things. That way, if (when) we break it, we don't disrupt the tools we rely on.
